==Swedish==
===Etymology===
The word was originally ''lögaredagen'', literally ''the cleaning day''.

===Noun===
'''lördag''' ''c'' (''plural'' [[lördagar]], ''definite singular'' [[lördagen]], ''definite plural'' [[lördagarna]], ''genitive singular'' [[lördags]], ''genitive singular definite'' [[lördagens]], ''genitive plural'' [[lördagars]], ''genitive plural definite'' [[lördagarnas]])

# [[Saturday]]. The sixth day of the [[week]] (according to the [[ISO]] 8601 [[standard]]).

